---

<span style="color:#3BB9FF">**Pillar**</span> is a collection of server recipies in Java, connected to random aspects of server-side processing, distributed interaction and connection management.

**pillar.common** - command line client, periodic tasks, abstract time provider, wait strategies, transactions abstraction.

**pillar.pulse** - abstract server heartbeat, provides information about other active servers running the same heartbeat.

**pillar.leadership**

**pillar.tracker**

**pillar.locks**

Detailed README for each subproject could be found in corresponding subfolders.
